rComments: Her lectures are dry and boring, and the concepts are not well-explained. In addition, the tests are full of minutiae that she mentions maybe once in one lecture. Overall, could probably put a cup of coffee to sleep.
Lecture slides are unclear, and the professor is not good at explaining the material so most of the time I have to read the textbook and try to learn everything by myself. Test and exam are okay.
HORRIBLE. DROP THE COURSE WHILE YOU CAN.
